data.description: Welcome to this stunning  Woodside-built home, nestled within the exclusive gated community of Sky Meadows. Immerse yourself in the luxury of single-story living with this meticulously crafted residence, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.25 baths and with a bonus room that can be convert into 4th bedroom or office space. Enter into a world of refined comfort as the open floor plan seamlessly connects the spacious living areas. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, adorned with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and upgraded cabinet space - a perfect blend of style and functionality. Indulge in the serenity of the large master suite. Pamper yourself in the spa-like bathroom with a separate tub and shower, dual sinks, and a walk-in closet that caters to your every need. This home is not only a masterpiece of design but equipped with a 12-panel solar system. Enjoy panoramic views of the foothills, creating a picturesque backdrop for your daily life. Nestled within the award-winning Clovis Unified School District. Seize the opportunity to call this Woodside gem home and elevate your lifestyle. Contact your realtor today to schedule a private tour today. Bed count different than tax records, buyer to verify if important.
